org.conqat.engine.sourcecode.coverage

Class CoverageProbeBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.engine.sourcecode.coverage.CoverageProbeBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public abstract class CoverageProbeBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Base class for coverage probes. Probes are generic coverage "indicators" associated with a source line (the start line of the corresponding statement). Probes can be of different types. For example in case of branch coverage a probe may indicate for an if condition how many times it was evaluated to true and how often to false.
